TASK_DESCRIPTION=Taskmaster message delivery to Subtaskmasters is unreliable. Observed: messages too long cause interrupts, doey-send retries multiple times, paste-buffer approach has timing issues, SM gets interrupted mid-prompt by repeated sends. The delivery path (doey-send.sh, load-buffer, paste-buffer, Enter) needs to be bulletproof — single attempt, confirmed delivery, no awkward retry loops.
